reviewText: We had seen this video some time ago, as a loaner from a local library.  For ALL ages, seeing this documentary on the contents of this regal doll house is a must!!
The video was very interesting and I plan to watch it again with some friends. The precise work that went into this Doll House is unbelieveable.
The most marvelous miniature I ever seen. This film shows all the details inside Queen Mary's dollhouse, and how they were done.
